    	<p><strong>Jonathan:</strong></p>
  		<p> Answers the following questions in a practice MMI:
  	
		<p><strong>1. What do you think about euthanasia?</strong>

		<p>2. You have only one dialysis machine available and three patients need it.  
		<p>One is a 17yr old drug addict who has taken an overdose, 
		<br>the second is a 40yr old woman with terminal breast cancer and 6 months to live and 
		<br>the third is a 70yr old marathon runner.  
		<strong><p>Who would you give the treatment to and why?</strong>

		<p>3.Teamwork is important in medicine. <p><strong>Are you a team leader or a follower?</strong>
		
		
		
		
    	
  		
